    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Yes, you need to use this:\n\n``` js\ninstantsearch.widgets.hits({\n  transformData: {\n    item: function() {},\n    empty: function() {}\n  }\n});\n```\n\nLet me know if this fixes the issue\n",
