    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "As pointed, `transformData` should be an object with `item` and `empty` keys. In previous versions of instantsearch, we allowed passing a function directly, as a shortcut for `transformData.item` but this will be deprecated.\n\nMaybe we have an example/tutorial/documentation somewhere with the old behavior. If that's the case, please give us the url so we can fix this :)\n",
